data.description: New listing! This 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home just hit the market.  Partial basement could be used as a 4th bedroom and has a half bath and it's own entrance that leads to the backyard.   New Roof installed in 2021.  Spacious 2 car garage.  Master bedroom has vaulted ceilings, walk in closet, bathroom with soaking tub and separate shower, vanity, lots of counter space and linen closet.  Kitchen is open to the Living room and Dining room and has a pantry.  Living room has fireplace with space above prepared for a flat screen.  Linen closet in hallway, closet under stairs, and pull down stairs to attic for extra storage space.  Located on a cul-de-sac-lot in Aragon just minutes from shopping and restaurants.  Call your Realtor today and schedule an appointment.
